1
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:58,670
With every sun comes a new day. A new beginning.
每次日出都意味着新的一天 新的开始

2
00:00:58,840 --> 00:01:02,586
A hope that things will be better today than they were yesterday.
希望今天会比昨天更好

3
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:06,136
But not for me. My name is Eep.
但对于我来说不是 我叫伊普

4
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:09,433
And this is my family, the Croods.
这是我的家人 我们是克鲁一家

5
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:11,979
If you weren't clued in already by the animal skins
如果你还没从我们的兽皮外衣和倾奇的前额

6
00:01:11,979 --> 00:01:14,453
and sloping foreheads, we're cavemen.
发现我们是谁的话 告诉你 我们是洞穴人

7
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:19,810
Most days we spend in our cave, in the dark.
我们大多宅在洞穴里 宅在黑暗里

8
00:01:20,473 --> 00:01:24,746
Night after night, day after day.
日复一日 夜复一夜地宅着

9
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:27,863
Yep, home sweet home.
对 温馨的家哪

10
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:31,107
When we did go out, we struggled to find food
一旦有机会出去 我们就想方设法

11
00:01:31,107 --> 00:01:33,720
in a harsh and hostile world.
在充满危险的世界中寻找食物

12
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:38,493
And I struggled to survive my family.
我则绞尽脑汁独自逃生

13
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:43,132
We were the last ones around. There used to be neighbors.
我们是最后的洞穴人了 曾经有其他的洞穴人

14
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:45,947
The Gorts, smashed by a mammoth.
高姿一家 被猛犸象一脚踩成肉泥

15
00:01:45,947 --> 00:01:48,570
The Horks, swallowed by a sand snake.
霍克一家 被沙蛇一口吞进肚里

16
00:01:48,570 --> 00:01:51,208
The Erfs, mosquito bite.
尔福一家 被蚊子活活咬死

17
00:01:51,208 --> 00:01:54,864
Throgs, common cold.
斯洛格一家 得个感冒就能死

18
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:58,036
And the Croods, that's us.
克鲁一家…就是我们啦

19
00:01:58,120 --> 00:02:01,428
The Croods made it, because of my dad.
我们活下来全靠我那爹

20
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:05,023
He was strong, and he followed the rules.
他死壮死壮的 特别循规蹈矩

21
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:07,789
The ones painted on the cave walls.
就是我们洞穴墙上的规矩

22
00:02:07,789 --> 00:02:10,395
Anything new is bad, curiosity is bad.
任何新事物都是不好的 好奇是不好的

23
00:02:10,395 --> 00:02:11,839
Going out at night is bad.
晚上外出是不好的

24
00:02:11,839 --> 00:02:13,968
Basically, anything fun is bad.
基本上任何有意思的事都是不好的

25
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,614
Welcome to my world.
欢迎来到我的苦逼世界

26
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:19,460
But this is a story about
但这故事要说的是

27
00:02:19,460 --> 00:02:21,806
how all that changed in an instant.
那一切怎样在瞬间全改变了

28
00:02:23,150 --> 00:02:26,022
Because what we didn't know was that our world...
因为我们不知道我们的世界

29
00:02:26,022 --> 00:02:28,308
was about to come to an end.
马上就要玩完了

30
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:33,018
And there were no rules on our cave walls to prepare us for that.
墙上可没有规矩教我们如何应付这种情况

31
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:55,621
You are supposed to wait for my signal. Eep?
你应该等我信号再出来的 小伊

32
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:00,647
Boo.
嘿

33
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:04,295
Ow! No!
不要！

34
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:12,229
We've been in that cave forever.
我们都在那破山洞里呆一万年了

35
00:03:12,229 --> 00:03:14,695
Three days is not forever.
三天可不是一万年

36
00:03:14,695 --> 00:03:16,517
It is with this family.
对于这个家就是

37
00:03:16,517 --> 00:03:21,039
Eep, would you come down here? You're being so dramatic.
小伊 给我下来呗？你太…招摇过市了

38
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,675
No, Sandy, come back here.
不 小沙 回来！

39
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:27,406
Remember the signal. Good girls wait for the signal. Ugga.
记住等信号 好姑娘都会等信号的 阿加！

40
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:31,861
As soon as I get Sandy, I'll go back in, and you can give the signal.
抓住小沙我就回去 你就可以发信号了

41
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:33,650
No, I mean, you're already out now.
不 但你们早出来了

42
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:35,216
I'm waiting for the signal, Dad.
我在等你信号的 爸爸！

43
00:03:35,216 --> 00:03:37,514
Never mind, Thunk. Just come out.
没事了 桑克 出来吧

44
00:03:37,514 --> 00:03:41,537
But if you don't give the signal, how do I know you're my dad?
但你要是不给我信号 我咋知道你是我爹？

45
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:43,152
The signal isn't so you know it's me.
信号不是让你知道是我

46
00:03:43,152 --> 00:03:45,691
It's so you know I wasn't eaten by an animal.
而是让你知道我没被动物吃掉

47
00:03:45,691 --> 00:03:48,278
Then why is the signal an animal noise?
那为什么信号是动物的声音呢？

48
00:03:48,278 --> 00:03:50,138
Doesn't that just confuse things?
我是说这难道不会使人产生误会？

49
00:03:50,138 --> 00:03:52,929
I don't know. I'm still waiting for the signal.
我还在等信号！

50
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:15,052
Mom, we're ready to leave.
妈妈 我们可以走了！

51
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,119
Mom?
妈妈？

52
00:04:19,520 --> 00:04:21,538
Still alive.
还没死呢！

53
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,618
It's still early.
还太早了

54
00:04:23,618 --> 00:04:25,569
And you're still fat.
你还这么肥

55
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,958
Breakfast formation!
排成早餐队形！

56
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:33,673
I want to see some real caveman action out there. We do this fast.
给我拿出点洞穴人的样子来！动作要快！

57
00:04:33,673 --> 00:04:36,586
We do this loud. We do this as a family.
声音要响 团结一致

58
00:04:37,673 --> 00:04:40,104
And never not be afraid!
学会害怕！

59
00:04:58,400 --> 00:05:00,239
Yay, breakfast.
耶…早餐耶…

60
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,934
Who's up?
该谁了？

61
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:20,796
We'll flip for it. Call her in the air.
投姥姥决定 扔上去

62
00:05:20,796 --> 00:05:21,952
Heads!
正面

63
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:25,859
Tails. Thunk is in. Positions.
反面 桑克上 就位！

64
00:05:25,859 --> 00:05:28,441
Okay. Thunk...
好 桑克

65
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,308
Go.
去吧！

66
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:33,597
Come on, Thunk.
快去 桑克！

67
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:41,918
Way to go. Take it to the cave.
太棒了！把它带回洞里！

68
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:48,309
Release the baby!
放孩子咬它！

69
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:50,343
Get them, Sandy! Go!
去吧 小沙 去吧！

70
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:15,179
Get them, Mom!
抓住他们 妈妈！

71
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:46,047
Old lady down! Eep, avenge me!
老太太失手！小伊 替我报仇！

72
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,100
Thanks.
谢谢

73
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,568
Eep!
小伊！

74
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,824
Heads up!
接好！

75
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,518
Hey Dad, can we eat now?
爸爸 现在可以吃了吗？

76
00:07:48,518 --> 00:07:50,568
Just wait till we get home.
回家再吃

77
00:07:50,568 --> 00:07:52,477
Eep, put on the brakes.
小伊 过来踩煞车！

78
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:15,397
Eep!
小伊！

79
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:38,947
- Who is hungry? - All right! Good one, Dad.
- 谁想吃？  - 干得好 爸爸

80
00:08:38,947 --> 00:08:40,777
Here you go, Thunk. Drink up.
给你 桑克 喝吧

81
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:46,691
- Sorry, Dad. - Looks like fast food tonight.
- 对不起 爸爸  - 看来得吃“快餐”了！

82
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:04,686
That's all right. I ate last week.
没事儿 我上周吃过了

83
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:10,346
Two knuckle warning!
两指节征兆！

84
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:12,141
Come on, Croods. Go, go.
快回去

85
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:19,337
Come on, come on. Darkness brings death. We know this.
快点 快点 黑暗会带来死亡！洞穴人都知道

86
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,766
The moon is full. Bath night.
月圆之夜 该洗澡喽

87
00:09:22,766 --> 00:09:24,695
- Run for your life! - You too, Mom.
- 逃命去！  - 休想跑 妈妈

88
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,798
I don't want to lose my protective layer.
我不想丢掉保护层！

89
00:09:27,798 --> 00:09:29,351
Mom, you've got ants.
妈妈 你都生蚂蚁了

90
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:33,357
See? Sandy doesn't fuss.
看 小沙都不跑

91
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:39,950
Is she still out there?
她还在外面？

92
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:41,867
You know she hates the cave, Grug.
你知道她讨厌呆在洞里 古勒格

93
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,562
Please come back tomorrow.
明天还要来哦

94
00:10:09,562 --> 00:10:12,911
How could she not like the cave? It's so cozy.
她怎么能不爱洞穴呢？这么温馨

95
00:10:12,911 --> 00:10:16,618
It is a little dark, Grug.
有点黑 不是吗？

96
00:10:16,618 --> 00:10:18,132
It's not that dark.
没那么黑啦

97
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,376
Eep!
小伊！

98
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:20,981
Eep?
小伊！

99
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:46,376
Come on, I have to close the cave.
快点 我要关门了

100
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,375
Eep!
小伊！

101
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:53,369
Okay, okay.
知道啦 来啦！

102
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:55,982
Come on.
快点

103
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:05,137
Eep! Come down!
小伊 下来！

104
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:25,785
- That was too close. - I was watching. I was fine.
- 太险了！  - 我看着呢 我没事

105
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:27,901
- What were you doing up there, Eep? - I don't know.
- 你去上面干什么 小伊？  - 不知道

106
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:29,420
- What were you looking for? - Nothing.
- 你去找什么？  - 没什么

107
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,377
- Then why did you go up there? - I don't know.
- 那你为什么上去？  - 不知道！

108
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:32,434
Why don't you know?
为什么不知道？

109
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:34,761
Stop looking for things.
别找东西了！

110
00:11:34,761 --> 00:11:38,356
Fear keeps us alive, Eep. Never not be afraid.
恐惧让我们活下来 小伊 永远要懂得害怕

111
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:41,170
What is the point of all this?
这一切有什么意义？

112
00:11:41,170 --> 00:11:42,680
What was that?
你说什么？

113
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:46,042
Why are we here? What are we doing this for?
我们为什么在这儿？我们这么做是为了什么？

114
00:11:49,040 --> 00:11:51,320
No one said survival was fun.
没人说过求生是好玩的

115
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,711
Nothing is fun.
没有什么是好玩的

116
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:55,012
- Would you come down here? - Grug.
- 你能不能下来 小伊？  - 古勒格？

117
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,727
- Eep. - Grug.
- 小伊  - 古勒格

118
00:11:55,727 --> 00:11:56,769
- Yes. - Off!
- 好  - 下来了

119
00:11:56,769 --> 00:11:58,727
- Yes, I know. Okay, I'm trying to... - Off.
- 好 我试过了  - 走开！

120
00:11:58,727 --> 00:12:01,189
I just don't see why she needs her own ledge, that's all.
我只是不懂她为什么需要独自呆着

121
00:12:01,189 --> 00:12:03,168
- That's what this is about. - She's working through some things...
- 只是想问问  - 她在想事情

122
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,949
and she needs her own space.
需要自己的空间

123
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:06,731
What things? How long is this going to take?
什么事？要多久？

124
00:12:06,731 --> 00:12:10,141
Really? She already doesn't listen to me. Hey!
真的吗？她都不听我说话了

125
00:12:10,141 --> 00:12:11,813
See? She's listening.
看 她听着呢

126
00:12:11,813 --> 00:12:14,809
If she wants to survive, she has to follow our rules.
要想幸存她就得遵守规矩

127
00:12:14,809 --> 00:12:17,235
How about a story? Eep loves those.
讲故事怎么样？小伊喜欢听故事

128
00:12:17,235 --> 00:12:19,106
That's a good ide... How about a story, huh?
好主意 想听故事吗？

129
00:12:19,106 --> 00:12:20,408
Yeah, tell us a story.
好耶 快讲

130
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:25,255
Okay. Can I borrow that? Thank you.
好 借用一下 谢谢

131
00:12:25,255 --> 00:12:28,222
Eep, your old favorite.
小伊！你以前的最爱！

132
00:12:28,222 --> 00:12:30,631
I haven't played with that thing in years.
我都好几年不玩了

133
00:12:30,631 --> 00:12:33,151
Tonight we'll hear the story of Krispy Bear.
今晚我们讲干脆熊的故事

134
00:12:33,151 --> 00:12:37,676
A long time ago, this little bear was alive.
很久很久以前 这只小熊还活着

135
00:12:37,676 --> 00:12:40,632
She was alive because she listened to her father...
她活着因为她听爸爸的话

136
00:12:40,632 --> 00:12:44,314
and lived her life in routine and darkness and terror.
在黑暗与恐惧中一成不变地生活着

137
00:12:44,460 --> 00:12:45,625
So she was happy.
所以她很快乐

138
00:12:46,280 --> 00:12:50,285
But Krispy had one terrible problem.
但干脆熊有个致命的问题

139
00:12:50,680 --> 00:12:54,722
She was filled with... curiosity.
她心中充满了…好奇

140
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:56,884
- Grug. - Yes. yes.
- 古勒格！  - 好 好

141
00:12:56,884 --> 00:13:00,030
And one day, while she was in a tree...
有一天 当她在树上的时候

142
00:13:00,030 --> 00:13:03,385
the curious little bear wanted to climb to the top.
这好奇的小熊想爬到树顶

143
00:13:03,385 --> 00:13:06,209
And no sooner than she climbed to the top...
她刚爬到树顶

144
00:13:06,209 --> 00:13:10,459
she saw something new and died!
就看见新奇的东西 然后就死了！

145
00:13:10,459 --> 00:13:12,411
- Just like that? - Yes!
- 就那样死了？  - 对！

146
00:13:12,411 --> 00:13:17,255
Her last moments of terror still frozen on her face.
她临死前的恐惧还凝结在脸上

147
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:18,541
Same ending as every day.
每天都一样的结局

148
00:13:18,400 --> 00:13:21,325
I get it, Dad. I will never do anything new or different.
懂了 爸爸 我绝不会尝试新事物的

149
00:13:21,325 --> 00:13:22,679
Good man, Thunk.
好孩子 桑克

150
00:13:22,315 --> 00:13:25,391
All right, everyone sharpen your teeth, and let's pile up.
好了 大家磨磨牙 叠一块儿睡觉吧

151
00:18:00,160 --> 00:18:01,556
Air.
憋死我了

152
00:18:01,556 --> 00:18:03,003
You talk.
你会说话

153
00:18:03,003 --> 00:18:04,835
I'm a person, like you.
我也是人 像你一样

154
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:09,789
Sort of like you.
和你…差不多吧

155
00:18:12,520 --> 00:18:13,702
Okay, okay.
行了

156
00:18:13,702 --> 00:18:14,797
Hey, hey, hey!
嘿 嘿 嘿

157
00:18:14,797 --> 00:18:16,420
Would you mind not...
你能不能…

158
00:18:19,080 --> 00:18:20,378
That tickles.
好痒啊

159
00:18:20,378 --> 00:18:21,812
Hey, hey, hey!
嘿 嘿 嘿！

160
00:18:24,920 --> 00:18:26,229
Quiet!
安静！

161
00:18:26,229 --> 00:18:28,097
I'm not supposed to be out here.
我是偷偷跑出来的

162
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:42,262
Eep is gone.
小伊不见了

163
00:18:42,262 --> 00:18:43,671
What? Grug!
什么？古勒格！

164
00:18:43,671 --> 00:18:44,660
Stay in the cave.
呆在洞里别动！

165
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:57,594
Wow. You are really strong.
你真强壮

166
00:19:01,040 --> 00:19:02,900
Hey! No! It's mine.
不！那是我的！

167
00:19:02,900 --> 00:19:04,194
- Please! Wait. - No!
- 求你了！  - 不！

168
00:19:04,194 --> 00:19:06,019
- It's dying! I can fix it! - No! I caught it!
- 快不行了 我能搞定  - 不！我发现的

169
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:07,955
Please! Please.
求你了

170
00:19:07,955 --> 00:19:09,456
I hate the dark.
我讨厌黑暗

171
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:20,850
Come on, come on, come on.
来吧 来吧…

172
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:25,747
It does what you tell it?
它这么听话？

173
00:19:25,747 --> 00:19:28,385
Yeah. Sort of.
嗯 算是吧

174
00:19:28,385 --> 00:19:29,678
The sun?
是太阳？

175
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:32,401
No, no, no. Fire.
不 不 是火

176
00:19:33,440 --> 00:19:35,926
Hi, fire.
你好啊 火

177
00:19:38,520 --> 00:19:40,315
It's not alive.
它没有生命

178
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,506
But you said it was dying.
但你说它要不行了

179
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:44,529
Sorry.
对不起

180
00:19:45,280 --> 00:19:47,450
It comes from where you come from?
你们来自同一个地方？

181
